Products.Name: Apple Mac Studio Z14K000AR M1 Ultra 20-core CPU 64-core GPU 128GB RAM 8TB SSD - Silver

Properties.Name: LongDescription
Properties.Value: Boost up your computing experience as the Apple Mac Studio M1 macOS CPU features the latest advancements delivering efficient performance. Mac Studio is a whole new Mac desktop experience. It crams incredible performance, broad connection, and new features into an incredibly small package, providing everything you need at your fingertips and transforming any room into a studio. The M1 Ultra allows you to run workflows on a massive scale. As a result, you may perform intricate particle simulations or work with enormous 3D environments that were previously unreachable. With double the media engine resources, the M1 Ultra can play up to 18 streams of 8K ProRes 422 video, which no other personal computer can match. With 12 high-performance ports situated front and rear for easy access, Mac Studio lets you construct the studio of your dreams. From the front, you can easily attach and unplug your camera, external storage, and other devices. Connect up to four Pro Display XDRs and one 4K TV to get a wider image. There's also a line out for amplified speakers or a headphone connector with improved compatibility for high-impedance headphones.
